These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, 7up
There 3 different types of food: grapes, avocado, nectarine
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, sports
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, argentine, italian
3 different pets are kept: pony, bird, guinea-pig
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, van, tram
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the far left##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the argentine is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person eating grapes is between the owner of the pony and the person eating avocado##2
8. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage      | 7up     | lemonade      | juice      |
| Food          | avocado   | grapes   | nectarine       |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | disaster | fantasy    |
| Nationality   | italian  | turkish    | argentine    |
| Pet           | bird    | guinea-pig    | pony |
| Transport     | van  | tram     | skateboard        |

