.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: potato, garlic, peas
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, thriller, comedy
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, japanese, australian
3 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit, bird
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, badminton
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person eating potato##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person eating peas is between the australian and the person drinking mirinda##2
7. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the owner of the bird##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk     | iced-tea        | mirinda      |
| Food          | garlic    | peas       | potato  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | thriller | romance    |
| Nationality   | australian | spanish   | japanese    |
| Pet           | rabbit      | fish  | bird      |
| Sport         | badminton    | snowboarding      | sailing |

