.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: lemon, tomato, lettuce
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, woodworking, gardening
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: indie, disco, house
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, german, australian
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goldfish, guinea-pig
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, tram, taxi
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the australian and the owner of the hedgehog##2
2. the german is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the japanese is the japanese##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the fan of disco##1
5. the german is on the left of the fan of indie##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person eating lemon##2
7. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the fan of disco is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
9. the person driving the tram is on the left of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |
| Food          | lemon  | tomato    | lettuce   |
| Hobby         | puzzles | gardening | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | house       | disco    | indie |
| Nationality   | australian    | german  | japanese  |
| Pet           | goldfish     | guinea-pig   | hedgehog       |
| Transport     | tram | subway     | taxi       |

