3. the person driving the subway is the italian##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the russian is on the right of the pakistani##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person eating lettuce and the person driving the jet-ski##2
9. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage      | coffee      | juice     | sprite      |
