2. the owner of the pony is the person eating pear##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
4. the thai is on the far right##1
5. the fan of pop is the owner of the cat##1
6. the doctor is between the person eating eggplant and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the dutch is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
8. the chef is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |      2       |       3       |
